{"tid":1368401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[花繼續開] 一群眼科視光師就近日社會議題之聯署聲明","createTime":"2019-07-26T13:07:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T15:12:47.000Z","uid":273907,"like":108,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"82f563eb0fcc43871274174af5e10e22f2c2b58d","tid":1368401,"uid":273907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:07:03.000Z","msg":"[代post]<br />\n致香港市民及政府:<br />\n<br />\n我們是普通市民，亦是一群熱心服務香港的眼科視光師。對於近日送中條例引發一連串事件，特別是元朗恐怖襲擊，我們感到極度憤怒及痛心， 對警察的執法及專業感到失望。而這些屢屢出現的社會運動亦反映特區政府管治和處理手法失當。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 警方面對暴力未能及時執法保護市民，更有包庇施襲者之嫌</strong><br />\n恐襲當日警方接到過萬求助電話，但反應緩慢。個別警務人員對白衣人士表現友好，開路讓他們離去，警署遇到大批市民報案時落閘，令人不禁質疑警方的執法能力，甚至有包庇縱容兇徒之嫌。對於村內白衣人士手持木棍而警方表示看不見任何武器，我們表示非常遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 警方摒棄專業</strong><br />\n作為醫療專業人士，眼科視光師秉持專業操守，即使政見不同，依然會緊守崗位，繼續服務市民，但警方卻因部分醫護人員對其表示不滿而撤離警崗;警方由 612 至今，已無數次使用催淚彈、催淚水劑，甚至布袋彈、橡膠子彈，多次水平射向只有防護裝備的示威者頭部，明顯使用過度武力，又多次拒絕展示委任證，違反警例。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 亂局起源為政府漠視民意</strong><br />\n民意之根本為市民，從過往DQ議員，選委會主任擅自判斷參選人資格已可見政府刻意限制市民聲音。日積月累下，直至修訂逃犯條例，意欲強行通過有違民意的法案，此舉成為壓毀駱駝的最後一根稻草。<br />\n<br />\n我們促請政府嚴正徹查事件，釐清警隊包庇黑社會的嫌疑，回復聲譽。然而，我們認為此一連串事件源於特區政府管治不當，議會失效，以及對警權缺乏機制抗衡。故此，我們強烈要求政府釋出善意，正面回應公眾及盡快實行雙普選，這才是能令社會回復平靜及修補裂痕的唯一方法。<br />\n<br />\n在此我們再重申五大訴求:<br />\n- 全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n- 撤銷 612 暴動定性<br />\n- 撤銷對示威者之檢控<br />\n- 成立獨立調查委員會徹查懷疑警黑勾結 ，及追究警察濫權<br />\n- 實行 2020 雙普選<br />\n缺一不可!香港加油!<br />\n<br />\n一群熱愛香港的眼科視光師上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J9tweCc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ9tweCc.png&h=45a1dc3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/39zGBQz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F39zGBQz.png&h=8c805067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/19YL3vB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F19YL3vB.png&h=88535382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0nARY3Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0nARY3Z.png&h=6aaf0f7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8G4Z7Xm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8G4Z7Xm.png&h=f5273629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QPqq3vK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQPqq3vK.png&h=6f64bc2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9RM53vN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9RM53vN.png&h=8fee87f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v7X5i39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv7X5i39.png&h=8302ff15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G3rNxpc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG3rNxpc.png&h=b1f2ec75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X6EZ7XA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX6EZ7XA.png&h=0faea683&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b732cc3af020d89add81c16d465d1816684929b2","tid":1368401,"uid":190604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:08:33.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d9a768114f60ec36182978bcdf71430fd9e6a0","tid":1368401,"uid":142332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:08:44.000Z","msg":"「工程界」遍地開花之踢走大白象工程<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1368270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1368270</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c155499f4a64a45d3e9d1f23cb517518838ade71","tid":1368401,"uid":262125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:09:07.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f587456d010adedf360c10a50675d4393868bae3","tid":1368401,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不枯也不散 我香港人終於可以紮根香港嗎"},{"pid":"bb4592b3365bb3dea12d37369cf53eb859c6f8e3","tid":1368401,"uid":114072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:11:20.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b974504b117eb84bc0bcfdb1a604b0d8eba409","tid":1368401,"uid":16610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:12:55.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"b5da331488c2d292f02e2ce035a63d0b47c0cfed","tid":1368401,"uid":38305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:12:58.000Z","msg":"光復香港時代革命"},{"pid":"9447602040f71da79adfc9fe7f6473b56420d2d8","tid":1368401,"uid":220723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:14:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b1a1bc3d0ea39e3c812f0f1a9d3291a6836dcf","tid":1368401,"uid":138296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:16:08.000Z","msg":"多謝"},{"pid":"9885a2e910f49da1a4a6fdc31b7a8de93bbf73e1","tid":1368401,"uid":98843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:17:00.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c99e66d2a647ee7b1a5ead0ba0bf1b84d893bf","tid":1368401,"uid":250147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又connected"},{"pid":"234b2d4831417881ef1e176cb4bbf8ee8c79e128","tid":1368401,"uid":170015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:57:36.000Z","msg":"林鄭又團結香港"},{"pid":"3d062a33effa16063a2259523ec19deac711e5c2","tid":1368401,"uid":50692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:11:45.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"981638c77c2a264fd0204694b1f5c8dd26ec512c","tid":1368401,"uid":70713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:26:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a23aef260773d94d0888f31f2637286b7c2ded2","tid":1368401,"uid":283764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:31:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af42d5d9929802580f50bbdb35d9d1f34fb4470f","tid":1368401,"uid":42393,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"82f563eb0fcc43871274174af5e10e22f2c2b58d","tid":1368401,"uid":273907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:07:03.000Z","msg":"[代post]<br />\n致香港市民及政府:<br />\n<br />\n我們是普通市民，亦是一群熱心服務香港的眼科視光師。對於近日送中條例引發一連串事件，特別是元朗恐怖襲擊，我們感到極度憤怒及痛心， 對警察的執法及專業感到失望。而這些屢屢出現的社會運動亦反映特區政府管治和處理手法失當。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 警方面對暴力未能及時執法保護市民，更有包庇施襲者之嫌</strong><br />\n恐襲當日警方接到過萬求助電話，但反應緩慢。個別警務人員對白衣人士表現友好，開路讓他們離去，警署遇到大批市民報案時落閘，令人不禁質疑警方的執法能力，甚至有包庇縱容兇徒之嫌。對於村內白衣人士手持木棍而警方表示看不見任何武器，我們表示非常遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 警方摒棄專業</strong><br />\n作為醫療專業人士，眼科視光師秉持專業操守，即使政見不同，依然會緊守崗位，繼續服務市民，但警方卻因部分醫護人員對其表示不滿而撤離警崗;警方由 612 至今，已無數次使用催淚彈、催淚水劑，甚至布袋彈、橡膠子彈，多次水平射向只有防護裝備的示威者頭部，明顯使用過度武力，又多次拒絕展示委任證，違反警例。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 亂局起源為政府漠視民意</strong><br />\n民意之根本為市民，從過往DQ議員，選委會主任擅自判斷參選人資格已可見政府刻意限制市民聲音。日積月累下，直至修訂逃犯條例，意欲強行通過有違民意的法案，此舉成為壓毀駱駝的最後一根稻草。<br />\n<br />\n我們促請政府嚴正徹查事件，釐清警隊包庇黑社會的嫌疑，回復聲譽。然而，我們認為此一連串事件源於特區政府管治不當，議會失效，以及對警權缺乏機制抗衡。故此，我們強烈要求政府釋出善意，正面回應公眾及盡快實行雙普選，這才是能令社會回復平靜及修補裂痕的唯一方法。<br />\n<br />\n在此我們再重申五大訴求:<br />\n- 全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n- 撤銷 612 暴動定性<br />\n- 撤銷對示威者之檢控<br />\n- 成立獨立調查委員會徹查懷疑警黑勾結 ，及追究警察濫權<br />\n- 實行 2020 雙普選<br />\n缺一不可!香港加油!<br />\n<br />\n一群熱愛香港的眼科視光師上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J9tweCc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ9tweCc.png&h=45a1dc3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/39zGBQz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F39zGBQz.png&h=8c805067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/19YL3vB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F19YL3vB.png&h=88535382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0nARY3Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0nARY3Z.png&h=6aaf0f7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8G4Z7Xm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8G4Z7Xm.png&h=f5273629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QPqq3vK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQPqq3vK.png&h=6f64bc2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9RM53vN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9RM53vN.png&h=8fee87f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v7X5i39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv7X5i39.png&h=8302ff15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G3rNxpc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG3rNxpc.png&h=b1f2ec75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X6EZ7XA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX6EZ7XA.png&h=0faea683&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:50:04.000Z","msg":"點解我收唔到消息<br />\n聽日自貼埋先"},{"pid":"c3c93fc15ededc2e7353b2aeedb060da29dd0538","tid":1368401,"uid":286781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:50:39.000Z","msg":"【投拆Hi】一人一信繼續投訴999，on L 9<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1368627\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1368627</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8238f30f4c4ae7845c9f09fb88fd95c4bf5fe29d","tid":1368401,"uid":290919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited